,('1985-12-25',5,2676,'To Hull and Back','Just a simple courier job says Boycie but the Trotter''s life on the ocean wave doesn''t go completely to plan. They run into their old friend Slater ''The Slag'' but it isn''t all plain sailing for him either.',0)
,('1986-08-31',1,2637,'From Prussia with Love','When a German damsel turns up in the Nag''s Head, she''s definitely in distress - and nine months pregnant at that. Rodney''s all beer and sympathy, but Del''s got an idea - could this be the answer to Boycie and Marlene''s dreams of a child and a golden opportunity to make a few bob along the way?',5)
